query:
SELECT DISTINCT t.id as tenant_id, t.name as company_name, u.email
FROM tenants t
LEFT JOIN users u ON u.tenantId = t.id
LEFT JOIN tenantSubscriptions ts ON ts.tenantId = t.id
WHERE ts.id IS NULL
ORDER BY t.id DESC
LIMIT 20;
